### =========================
### PUBLIC ANNOUNCEMENTS
### =========================

### GET all
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements

###

### GET search
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements?search=asus

###

### GET sort/page
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements?sort=oldest&page=1

###

### GET existing id
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements/1

###

### GET non existing id
GET http://localhost:3000/announcements/99999


### =========================
### AUTH
### =========================

### REGISTER
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan123",
  "password": "123456",
  "name": "Іван"
}

###

### LOGIN
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan123",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### LOGIN invalid credentials
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ivan123",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### GET current user
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### REFRESH TOKEN
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

###

### LOGOUT
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN


### =========================
### PROTECTED ANNOUNCEMENTS
### =========================

### CREATE announcement
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Продам ноутбук ASUS",
  "description": "Відмінний стан, 16GB RAM",
  "price": 18000,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "0991234567"
}

###

### CREATE announcement without token (401)
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test",
  "description": "Test description",
  "price": 100,
  "category": "sale",
  "contactInfo": "0991234567"
}

###

### CREATE invalid announcement
POST http://localhost:3000/announcements
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "ABC"
}

###

### UPDATE own announcement
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 20000
}

###

### UPDATE non existing announcement
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/99999
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 20000
}

###

### UPDATE чужого оголошення (403)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer OTHER_USER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 99999
}

###

### DELETE own announcement
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### DELETE non existing announcement
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/99999
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

###

### DELETE чужого оголошення (403)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/announcements/1
Authorization: Bearer OTHER_USER_TOKEN
